{title: Original Key}
{key: C}

{start_of_verse}
[C]Playing in the [F]key of [G]C
[Am]Natural and [F]easy as can [G]be
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]Simple [C]chords, [G]simple [Am]song
[F]In the key of [G]C where I be[C]long
{end_of_chorus}

{new_song}

{title: Transposed Up}
{key: C}
{transpose: 3}

{start_of_verse}
[C]Same song but [F]transposed up [G]three
[Am]Now in the [F]key of [G]Eb
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]Simple [C]chords, [G]simple [Am]song
[F]Transposed up [G]three where they be[C]long
{end_of_chorus}

{new_song}

{title: Transposed Down}
{key: C}
{transpose: -2}

{start_of_verse}
[C]Same song but [F]transposed down [G]two
[Am]Now in the [F]key of [G]Bb
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]Simple [C]chords, [G]simple [Am]song
[F]Transposed down [G]two all along [C]
{end_of_chorus}
